## Data Source Licenses

This project aggregates data from multiple sources, each with their own licenses:

- **GBIF Data**: Licensed under CC0 1.0 or CC-BY 4.0 (varies by dataset)
  - Citation required for published use
  - https://www.gbif.org/terms

- **Wikimedia Commons**: Varies by image (CC-BY, CC-BY-SA, Public Domain)
  - Check individual image licenses
  - https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:Licensing

- **Wikipedia**: CC-BY-SA 3.0
  - Attribution required
  - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Copyrights

- **Trefle API**: Check Trefle.io terms of service
  - https://trefle.io

- **Encyclopedia of Life**: Varies by content provider
  - https://eol.org/docs/what-is-eol/data-services/classic-apis

- **iNaturalist**: Varies by observation (user-set licenses)
  - https://www.inaturalist.org/pages/help#licenses

- **Laji.fi**: Check Finnish Biodiversity Info Facility terms
  - https://laji.fi

- **Biodiversity Heritage Library**: Public Domain or out-of-copyright material
  - https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/gethelp#Copyright

Users of this software must comply with the licenses of all data sources used.
